[3]
Date: Fri 7 Jun 2002
From: Jean Paul Durand <imtssa.vro@wanadoo.fr>

Djbouti: Increase of Dengue Fever among French Troops
-----------------------------------------------------
An arbovirus survey of French troops in Djibouti showed for the 2
months of April and May 2002 an increase of fevers with positive IgM
dengue serology. We isolated this week in Marseille 5 strains of
dengue virus serotype 1 from the frozen peripheral blood cells of 9
patients.
--
J. P. Durand, MD
Unit of Virology
BP 46 -- Le Pharo- IMTSSA
13997 Marseille Armees
